text: Homfray is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Don Homfray (1935–2012), production designer * Francis Homfray (1725–1798), industrialist * Jeremiah Homfray (1759–1833), ironmaster * Samuel Homfray (1762–1822), industrialist ==See also== * Phillips v Homfray, lawsuit
